  <brief_title>Measurement of a Systolic Pressure Index at the Toe After a Walking Test</brief_title>
  <acronym>IPSO FACTO</acronym>
  <official_title>Validation of the Measurement of a Systolic Pressure Index at the Toe (IPSO) After a Walking Test</official_title>
