2 hours of rest.
BBP-LR and the blood pressure at the left and right ankles (BPA-LR) are measured.
WT is reperformed.
BBP-LR and BPA-LR are re-measured.</description>
    <arm_group_label>Healthy Volunteers 2</arm_group_label>
